77","tid":13264,"uid":31019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:28:48.000Z","msg":"[img]圖片網址 [/img]<a href=\"http://www.google.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com&d=SosmRuku1xQpFtIKZJ5auQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=da858d74\" target=\"_blank\">www.google.com</a><blockquote>我有一個大西瓜</blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我有一個大西瓜</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><del><strong>我有一個大西瓜<em></em></strong></del></span>"},{"pid":"b3bdae526e7bdc1eede353b55a4fd003efc3ac42","tid":13264,"uid":31019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:31:09.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">😨</div><br />\n<ul><br />\n[*]👳🏻<br />\n<ul><br />\n[*]👲<br />\n</ul><br />\n</ul><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">💩</span></strong>"},{"pid":"54c2a06dd3fddc42d4a807616c1333fbed158175","tid":13264,"uid":31019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:33:49.000Z","msg":"<ins>鏢局，現代保安運輸的前身，起源於明朝年間，以受人錢財代運送貨物至目的地為主，由於途經之路必遇官家、黑道，成功的鏢局除了要有好功夫，不論黑白二道都需要一定人緣關係。</ins><br />\n<br />\n鏢局接單運送稱作「走鏢」，通常會以「威武鏢」、「仁義鏢」或「偷鏢」形式運送，三者分別在於「響朵」、「半響朵」或「唔響朵」。<br />\n<br />\n時至今天，除了解款車比較近似鏢局的運作，古時形式的鏢局可謂已經絕種，至少我曾是這樣認為。<br />\n<br />\n半年之前，我繼承了一筆遺產，事源是伯父離世，未結婚、膝下無兒的他竟把所有資產指定留給我，此事全家上下都大感意外。<br />\n<br />\n伯父生前與家人關係極差，主要是因為伯父從年少起就撈偏，早年常給家裡帶來麻煩，聽父親說家裡常有警察上門，頻密得後來姑姐竟嫁了給其中一個警員。<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>大概伯父也知道家人受不了，他與家裡斷絕來往，除了有時逢年過節祖父祖母會收到匿名款項，數十年來他也真的始終沒露面。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/threeformthree\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fthreeformthree&d=SosmRuku1xQpFtIKZJ5auQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=32f915cc\" target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/threeformthree</a>"},{"pid":"f68d6be92202f9c333c4beb69f6e0ef683673629","tid":13264,"uid":44339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:42:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class